  "text": "Cell proliferation was detected by the MTS assay (Promega, Madison, WI, USA) as reported in [CITATION_1] . Briefly, cell cultures in 96-well plate were incubated at 100 l medium with 20 l of CellTiter 96 AQueous One Solution reagent for 3-4 h. The cell viability was determined. The growth rate was calculated from the absorbance and was normalized.",
